      "jurisdiction": ["VA"],
      "year_field_label": "Fiscal year (FY ends Jun 30)",
      "y_axis_label": "External Review requests (VA SCC BOI)",
      "caveat_short": "Health external-review dispositions — managed-care coverage appeals only. Pre-filtered for adjudicability (ineligible cases excluded from on-merits pool), so the against-rate runs much higher (~54%) than overall regulator-finding rates would. Don't compare directly to MD MIA's 5.68% — different denominators.",
